     Wyatt Earp calls on Dodge City Sheriff Bat Masterson (George Montgomery) to track down a rancher who is accused of murder. Thanks, however, to some evidence held by the Indian chief Yellow Hawk (Jay Silverheels), Masterson realizes Merrick might be the victim of a frame-up.
